paragraphs.title: Check CUDA Version
paragraphs.text:
%sh
#ToBeCompared
python <<END
import subprocess
a = subprocess.check_output('/usr/local/cuda/bin/nvcc --version',shell=True,stderr=subprocess.STDOUT)
if 'V8.0.44' in a:
    print(True)
else:
    print(False)
END

paragraphs.title: Check CUDN Version
paragraphs.text:
%sh
#ToBeCompared
python <<END
import subprocess
a = subprocess.check_output('cat /usr/local/cuda/include/cudnn.h | grep CUDNN_MAJOR',shell=True,stderr=subprocess.STDOUT)
if 'CUDNN_MAJOR      6' in a:
    print(True)
else:
    print(False)
END
